# Cursor Rules for Samwise Project

## Documentation Policy

- NEVER create new summary files (e.g., SUMMARY.md, IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md, etc.)
- NEVER create additional README files beyond the main README.md
- NEVER create .txt summary files
- Keep documentation minimal and focused
- Only update existing README.md or AGENT.md when needed
- Do not create documentation for every change or feature

## Allowed Documentation Files

- README.md - Main project documentation
- AGENT.md - Developer/agent guide
- .cursorrules - This file

## Code Changes

- Focus on code implementation, not documentation
- Keep commit messages concise
- Prefer working code over extensive docs

